      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_9163134593740134051.png",
                "key": "溯因反绎法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "溯因反绎法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光镜</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/8491b6dd997a8a4878767f1191a2b6aa_1384963506953616422.png",
                "key": "共相·理式摹写",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "共相·理式摹写"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光镜</span>，此伤害提升所消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光镜</span>的持续回合值。</p><p>如果消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光镜</span>的持续回合为0/1/2, 则为角色附属持续回合为3/2/1的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琢光镜</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/a3b3108e0046cb101533a3bf6dcbe717_2996681912575077089.png",
                "key": "殊境·显象缚结",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "殊境·显象缚结"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>。</p><p>角色普通攻击后：造成1点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>。如果此技能为<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重击</span>，则使状态的持续回合+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合：2</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到3回合）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1103834717756221475.png",
                "key": "琢光镜",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "琢光镜"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span>]</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_1853945109009876225.png",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重击</span></strong></p><p>我方开始行动前，如果元素骰总数为偶数，则进行的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「普通攻击」</span>将被视为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「重击」</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4193403505706742627.png",
